name: TheAtlantic
text: Meet the Milk Tea Alliance, the very online grouping that is emblematic of the frustration many young people feel toward Beijing’s grating assertiveness in Asia. @TMcLaughlin3 reports: https://t.co/3l7Q0WyAYD

name: TheAtlantic
text:
RT @JeffreyGoldberg: "Although there are no clearly documented cases of coronavirus transmission via woodwind, there is a lot of evidence of the benefit of kids studying musical instruments, and taking part in team-based competition."

name: TheAtlantic
text:
RT @YasmeenSerhan: "Although I am aware of how important it is for Americans to fight to save their democracy in this perilous moment, if I hadn’t already left, I’d be sorely tempted to leave now." 

Read @mirakamdar on why she left America for France:

name: TheAtlantic
text: "There hasn’t been a day since Donald Trump was elected in 2016 that I haven’t been thankful that I live in France, and not in the United States," @mirakamdar writes: https://t.co/QM2NTwynYV
